<div id="message_search">
  <h2>Share with My Feed</h2>
  <% form_tag providers_path, :method => :get do %>
    <%= text_area_tag(:search, nil, {:cols => 87, :rows => 5, :class => "left"} )%>
    <div id="search_buttons">
      <%= submit_tag "Send", :name => nil, :class => 'medium_btn tip', :title => "Send Message" %>
      <%= link_to "Clear", "", :id => "search_clear", :class => "tip", :title => "Clear Message Box" %>
    </div>
    <% end %>
    <div class="clear"></div>
    <div class="paperclip_link">
      <div class="green_paper_clip"></div>
      <%= link_to "Attach File", "", :id => "message_attach_link", :class => "tip", :title => "Attach a File" %>
      <div id="message_attachment" style="display: none;">
        <%= file_field :attachment, :size => 16 %>
      </div>
      <div class="clear"></div>
    </div>
</div>
<h2 class="content_header">My Feed</h2>
<div id="center_message_content_wrap">
  <div class="message_feed_main">
    <div class="image_wrap">
      <%= image_tag('message/avatar_jason_pierson.jpg', :alt => "Jason Pierson Avatar") %>
    </div>
    <div class="message_wrap">
      <h3 class="green">Kim Young:</h3>
      <p>Along with the AHIP documents from our meeting, I understand that Paul and Kate put together a storyboard. Could I get that to review before I leave at tomorrow at 3 p.m.</p>
      <div class="message_links">
        <span>24 minutes ago</span> <span class="text_spacer">|</span><span class="green"><%= link_to "Reply", "", :rel => "#coming_soon", :class => "green tip coming_soon", :title => "Reply to this post" %></span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="message_reply">
      <div class="image_wrap">
        <%= image_tag('message/avatar_darin_johnson_small.jpg', :alt => "Darin Johnson Small Avatar") %>
      </div>
      <div class="reply_message_wrap">
        <h3 class="green">Paul White:</h3>
        <p>Attached is the AHIP storyboard. You can also touch base with Kate if you see a need for any adjustments. She is moving forward with any needed updates.</p>
        <div class="message_links">
          <span>18 minutes ago</span>
        </div>
        <div class="attachment_wrap">
          <div class="gray_paper_clip"></div>
          <span class="text_spacer left">1 attachment |</span>
          <div class="attachment left">
            <%= link_to "ahip_storyboard.pdf", "", :rel => "#coming_soon", :class => "green tip coming_soon", :title => "Download PDF" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="message_feed_main">
    <div class="image_wrap">
       <%= image_tag('message/avatar_brian_smith.jpg', :alt => "Brian Johnson Avatar") %>
    </div>
    <div class="message_wrap">
      <h3 class="green">Kate Grua:</h3>
      <p>We've received some great feedback from our latest test group about the updates that were made to the Claims reporting. The ease of use is saving time and budget.</p>
      <div class="message_links">
        <span>over 1 hour ago</span> <span class="text_spacer">|</span><span class="green"><%= link_to "Reply", "", :rel => "#coming_soon", :class => "green tip coming_soon", :title => "Reply to this post" %></span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="message_reply">
      <div class="image_wrap">
        <%= image_tag('message/avatar_darin_johnson_small.jpg', :alt => "Paul White Small Avatar") %>
      </div>
      <div class="reply_message_wrap">
        <h3 class="green">Paul White:</h3>
        <p>Let's shoot for including that feedback in the Q2 report. The initial round should be finished by next Wednesday.</p>
        <div class="message_links">
          <span>48 minutes ago</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>